{"tid":2069251,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Vdada脫醣電飯煲一問","createTime":"2020-06-18T08:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T16:13:03.000Z","uid":241915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"544b2239cddad5f1dfbf1e0dc636084bf13223b8","tid":2069251,"uid":241915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T08:59:39.000Z","msg":"我媽係香城用680蚊買左個返屋企，<br />\n食落同普通飯冇分別<br />\n煲又要成半個鐘<br />\n其實係咪有料到？"},{"pid":"279a32d47f1a7e3d432927a4ddbaeb5b991a6ffb","tid":2069251,"uid":169116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:49:14.000Z","msg":"其實你買個蒸籠蒸飯咪一樣。"},{"pid":"282651eef5bbc2c0ab8af02cc80495474b3c9379","tid":2069251,"uid":241817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:49:52.000Z","msg":"食少d飯多d餸仲實際"},{"pid":"c32397a88f5bef43b4942894e059001ddaa64072","tid":2069251,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:54:37.000Z","msg":"唔食飯咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815e0c71fc00d750fed457883fbbd45b7691fd88","tid":2069251,"uid":36995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:55:01.000Z","msg":"你老母俾TVB呃鳩左"},{"pid":"47340248e0b30ce01d0efa6e51728ccddb208536","tid":2069251,"uid":7331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T12:35:02.000Z","msg":"喺facebook好多廣告<br />\n<br />\n支那野扮日本野？"},{"pid":"a50a426d3295fa65abfb4355fa856d10766400d5","tid":2069251,"uid":52056,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQK421bSezCHO24yyFEkY9eZA07UK4fcoc7L2K0ZGP6gxwK5SJV&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcQK421bSezCHO24yyFEkY9eZA07UK4fcoc7L2K0ZGP6gxwK5SJV%26usqp%3DCAU&h=20f70b79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n醣呢隻字即係碳水化合物咁解，而米粒嘅碳水化合物就係澱粉<br />\n白米係米粒儲存澱粉嘅部份，因為結構鬆散所以澱粉微粒好易俾水洗走<br />\n浸米嗰陣(左圖)啲水浸過米粒，白米表面嘅澱粉會俾水帶走，煲嘢變成洗多一次嘅米+洗米水<br />\n煮飯嗰陣(右圖)水份受熱蒸發，水位下降，含有澱粉嘅水就會積喺裝飯個內膽下面，煲嘢變成蒸飯+煮過嘅洗米水<br />\n<br />\n一句講晒，用脫醣飯煲同你洗多兩次米無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62a2abcba162fc6c2db55e1b2129f3aacc96796","tid":2069251,"uid":299794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T16:13:03.000Z","msg":"其實咪又係蒸飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}